            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "Consumo global por mercado:\n(M1,3.580541891E9)\n(M2,3.6993274255E9)\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.types._\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrddCrudo\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.rdd.RDD[String]\u001b[0m \u003d file:///opt/spark/data/endesaAgregada MapPartitionsRDD[1] at textFile at \u003cconsole\u003e:36\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrddSeleccionado\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.rdd.RDD[(String, String, String, String, String, Array[Double])]\u001b[0m \u003d MapPartitionsRDD[2] at map at \u003cconsole\u003e:40\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrddLimpio\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.rdd.RDD[(String, String, String, String, String, Array[Double])]\u001b[0m \u003d MapPartitionsRDD[3] at filter at \u003cconsole\u003e:57\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrddProcesado\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.rdd.RDD[(String, String, String, String, String, Double)]\u001b[0m \u003d MapPartitionsRDD[4] at map at \u003cconsole\u003e:63\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrddTotalPorMercad...\n"
          }
        ]
