        "code": "SUCCESS",
        "msg": [
          {
            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "Consulta A (Tipada) - Consumo Nocturno frente a Madrugada en Mercado M1:\n+------+--------+--------------------------+\n|ANOMES|PRODUCTO|Diferencia_Noche_Madrugada|\n+------+--------+--------------------------+\n|201507|      P1|                   18896.0|\n|201411|      P1|                   13577.5|\n|201412|      P1|                   13164.0|\n|201507|      P1|                   12540.0|\n|201411|      P2|                   11745.0|\n+------+--------+--------------------------+\nonly showing top 5 rows\n\nConsulta B (Tipada) - Suma total de consumo a la Hora de Comer (H14) por Producto:\n+----+------------------------+\n| key|ReduceAggregator(double)|\n+----+------------------------+\n|P110|                 30380.0|\n| P62|               3683191.0|\n|P118|                  5158.5|\n| P72|                106126.5|\n| P13|            6.69090385E7|\n| P96|                  3381.0|\n| P59|                271701.0|\n| P74|                 18218.0|\n| P30|            2.27564595E7|\n| P87|                103931.5|\n|P119|                 20346.5|\n| P82|                 41800.5|\n| P23|               1895623.0|\n| P61|                  1000.5|\n|  P2|               8855184.0|\n|P111|                 38172.0|\n| P75|                325803.5|\n|P117|                  5345.5|\n| P67|                 22062.0|\n| P71|                  4700.5|\n+----+------------------------+\nonly showing top 20 rows\n\nimport spark.implicits._\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mdsConsumo\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[ConsumoElectrico]\u001b[0m \u003d [IDENTIFICADOR: string, ANOMES: int ... 27 more fields]\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mdsMercadoRegulado\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[ConsumoElectrico]\u001b[0m \u003d [IDENTIFICADOR: string, ANOMES: int ... 27 more fields]\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mdsAnalisisImpacto\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame\u001b[0m \u003d [ANOMES: int, PRODUCTO: string ... 1 more field]\n\u001b[